Grab gnuplot3.8k tarball

Copy and rename the new gnuplot adapter to term/aquaterm.trm (NB. no upper case 'T')

edit configure manually. Look for the line
LIBS="$LIBS -framework Foundation -framework AppKit" and replace it by
LIBS="$LIBS -laquaterm -framework Foundation"

./configure
make
make install

If you plan on running long sessions with gnuplot, you also want to apply this patch (prevents incresing memory hogging).

Copy the diff below and apply it (in gnuplot dir) using:
patch <path/to/diff

--- cut here ---
